cmd : npm init -y --> install package.json
cmd : npm install typescrit --save-dev --> install typescript with dev dependancie
cmd : npm install -D tailwindcss@3 -->> install tailwindcss
cmd : npx tsc --init --> initialization of typescript
cmd : npx tailwindcss init --> initalization of tailwindcss

on package.jon '"scripts" :{
    "build:css": "tailwind -i ./src/styles.css -o ./dist/styles.css --watch"
}' --> create script to compile css

on tsconfig.json add '"outDir": "./src", ' and '"rootDir": "./src",' --> configure your src files for typescript

on tsconfig.json add '"scripts" : {
    "build:css": "tailwindcss -i ./src/styles.css -o ./dist/styles.css --watch",
    "build:ts": "tsc --watch"
  }' --> script to compile typescript
  
  for fedora user : 
  	sudo setenforce 0 (before make) >> desactivate SELinux which control every processus permissions (sooo not good for security to desactivate but for docker which is not on fedora it's necessary)
	sudo setenforce 1 (after work)